	<div class="flex flex-col items-start w-full gap-3">
		<div class="flex flex-col">
			<div class="w-full px-2 py-1 text-2xl text-white bg-black font-neue-haas-grotesk">
				about me
			</div>
			<div class="p-2.5 flex flex-row items-start w-full border border-black">
				<p>
					yo, i&apos;m ty, aka tygrdev <span class="text-neutral-500">[or tygrxqt if you know me well enough]</span>. welcome to my form of virtual self-expression.
					<br /><br />
