					building truely open alternative software and services for people who <i>care</i>. i'm currently a full stack software engineer at <Link href="https://circle.cloud">circle.cloud</Link> and i also founded <Link href="https://nordstud.io">Nord Studio</Link> and <Link href="https://masonrystudio.co.uk">Masonry Studio</Link>.
					<br /><br />
					you can reach me via the <Link href="https://nordstud.io/discord">Nord Studio Discord</Link>, or via email at hi (at) tygr (dot) dev for any questions, help with my work, or if you wanna say "hiii :3"
